{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0004_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0004", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["躁煩"], "pulse": ["數", "靜", "數急"], "time_course": ["一日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["傳", "為傳也", "不傳"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒一日，太陽受之，脈若靜者，為不傳。頗欲吐，若躁煩，脈數急者，為傳也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.872, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0005_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0005", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": [], "pulse": [], "time_course": ["二三日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["不傳"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒二三日，陽明、少陽證不見者，為不傳也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.832, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0008_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0008", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["太陽病"], "symptoms": ["頭痛"], "pulse": [], "time_course": ["七日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["不傳"]}, "evidence_span": "太陽病，頭痛至七日以上自愈者，以行其經盡故也。若欲作再經者，針足陽明，使經不傳則愈。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.852, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0097_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0097", "six_channel": "太陽病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": ["往來寒熱", "不欲飲食", "嘔", "渴"], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["屬陽明"]}, "evidence_span": "血弱氣盡，腠理開，邪氣因入，與正氣相搏，結於脅下，正邪分爭，往來寒熱，休作有時，嘿嘿不欲飲食，藏府相連，其痛必下，邪高痛下，故使嘔也，小柴胡湯主之。服柴胡湯已，渴者屬陽明，以法治之。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.872, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0181_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0181", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["陽明病", "太陽病"], "symptoms": ["大便難"], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["轉屬", "屬陽明"]}, "evidence_span": "問曰：何緣得陽明病？答曰：太陽病，若發汗，若下，若利小便，此亡津液，胃中乾燥，因轉屬陽明。不更衣，內實，大便難者，此名陽明也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.872, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0184_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0184", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["陽明病"], "symptoms": ["惡寒"], "pulse": [], "time_course": ["二日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["傳"]}, "evidence_span": "問曰：惡寒何故自罷？答曰：陽明居中，主土也，萬物所歸，無所復傳，始雖惡寒，二日自止，此為陽明病也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.852, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0185_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0185", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["發熱", "無汗", "嘔", "不能食", "反汗出"], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["轉屬", "屬陽明"]}, "evidence_span": "本太陽，初得病時，發其汗，汗先出不徹，因轉屬陽明也。傷寒發熱，無汗，嘔不能食，而反汗出濈濈然者，是轉屬陽明也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.872, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0188_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0188", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒"], "symptoms": ["濈然微汗出"], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["轉繫"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒轉繫陽明者，其人濈然微汗出也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.852, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0243_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0243", "six_channel": "陽明病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": ["食穀欲嘔"], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["屬陽明"]}, "evidence_span": "食穀欲嘔，屬陽明也，吳茱萸湯主之；得湯反劇者，屬上焦也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.832, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0266_002", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0266", "six_channel": "少陽病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["太陽病"], "symptoms": ["脅下硬滿", "乾嘔", "不能食", "往來寒熱"], "pulse": ["沉緊"], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["轉入"]}, "evidence_span": "本太陽病不解，轉入少陽者，脅下硬滿，乾嘔不能食，往來寒熱，尚未吐下，脈沉緊者，與小柴胡湯。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.872, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_0384_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_0384", "six_channel": "霍亂病", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["傷寒", "霍亂"], "symptoms": ["嘔", "下利", "能食", "反不能食"], "pulse": ["微", "澀微"], "time_course": ["四五日", "十三日", "一日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["轉入", "屬陽明"]}, "evidence_span": "傷寒，其脈微澀者，本是霍亂，今是傷寒，卻四五日，至陰經上，轉入陰必利；本嘔，下利者，不可治也。欲似大便，而反失氣，仍不利者，此屬陽明也，便必硬，十三日愈。所以然者，經盡故也。下利後，當便硬，硬則能食者愈。今反不能食，到後經中，頗能食，復過一經能食，過之一日當愈；不愈者，不屬陽明也。", "evidence_type": "original_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.812, "release_level": "silver"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_AUX_0045_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_AUX_0045", "six_channel": "", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": [], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["傳"]}, "evidence_span": "師曰：子之所問，道之根源。脈有三部，尺寸及關；榮衛流行，不失衡銓；腎沉心洪，肺浮肝弦；此自經常，不失銖分；出入升降，漏刻周旋；水下二刻，一周循環；當復寸口，虛實見焉；變化相乘，陰陽相干；風則浮虛，寒則牢堅；沉潛水畜，支飲急弦；動則為痛，數則熱煩；設有不應，知變所緣；三部不同，病各異端；太過可怪，不及亦然；邪不空見，中必有奸；審察表裏，三焦別焉；知其所舍，消息診看；料度府藏，獨見若神。為子條記，傳與賢人。", "evidence_type": "auxiliary_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.712, "release_level": "bronze"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_AUX_0112_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_AUX_0112", "six_channel": "", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": ["太陽病", "陽明病", "少陽病", "太陰病", "少陰病", "厥陰病"], "symptoms": ["頭痛", "身熱", "耳聾", "渴"], "pulse": [], "time_course": ["七日", "八日", "九日", "十日", "十一日", "十二日"]}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["不傳"]}, "evidence_span": "其不兩感於寒，更不傳經，不加異氣者，至七日太陽病衰，頭痛少愈也；八日陽明病衰，身熱少歇也；九日少陽病衰，耳聾微聞也；十日太陰病衰，腹減如故，則思飲食；十一日少陰病衰，渴止舌乾，已而嚏也；十二日厥陰病衰，囊縱，少腹微下，大氣皆去，病人精神爽慧也。", "evidence_type": "auxiliary_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "warn", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.772, "release_level": "bronze"}}
{"initial_rule_id": "IR_SHL_AUX_0120_001", "clause_id": "SHL_SONGBEN_AUX_0120", "six_channel": "", "rule_type": "transformation_rule", "if_conditions": {"disease": [], "symptoms": [], "pulse": [], "time_course": []}, "then_conclusions": {"transmission": ["傳"]}, "evidence_span": "凡作湯藥，不可避晨夜，覺病須臾，即宜便治，不等早晚，則易愈矣。若或差遲，病即傳變，雖欲除治，必難為力。服藥不如方法，縱意違師，不須治之。", "evidence_type": "auxiliary_text", "interpretation": "本條論六經傳變或不傳之判斷。", "interpretation_level": "normalized", "model_confidence": 0.8, "prescription_strength": "", "autonomous_review": {"evidence_verified": true, "schema_valid": true, "semantic_result": "pass", "critic_result": "pass", "critic_flags": [], "repairs": [], "consensus_score": 0.772, "release_level": "bronze"}}
